# Assets Loans And Receivables Current Insurance And Other Recoveries Provision For Doubtful Debts Amount

## identifier
de8978

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of provision for doubtful debts in relation to insurance and other recoveries that are classified as current in accordance with relevant accounting standards.

Insurance and other recoveries may consist of subrogation, salvage or other recoveries.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Assets.LoansAndReceivables.CurrentInsuranceAndOtherRecoveriesProvisionForDoubtfulDebts.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo5.02.06
- period=instant
